text: Maria Dolors Renau, 2009 Maria Dolors Renau i Manén (15 November 1936 – 29 August 2019) was a Spanish politician who served as a Deputy and an MEP, as well as president of Socialist International Women (1999–2003). Renau died in Sant Cugat del Vallès on 29 August 2019 at the age of 82. ==References== Category:1936 births Category:2019 deaths Category:Spanish politicians
